title: 2015 Prom Dresses: White, Gold and Blue Prom Dresses | Lord & Taylor
description:
Shop 2015 prom dresses at Lord & Taylor. Find statement-making prom gowns in white, gold and blue. Pair a clutch that can hold the essentials & you'll be ready for the #bestnightever!

Style Tip #1: A top-knot is a fun, youthful way to balance the drama of a statement-making gown.
Style Tip #2: Make sure your clutch can comfortably hold the essentials - a phone, credit card, comb and lipstick or gloss.
